---
---

<!-- About Company Section -->
<section class="py-32 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
      <span class="text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-brand-blue font-bold mb-4 block">About Us</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-brand-text tracking-tight mb-6">Who We Are</h2>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-left space-y-6">
        <p class="text-brand-text/80 font-normal leading-relaxed">
          Alexis Employment Pte Ltd is an established, MOM-licensed maid agency in Singapore, committed to delivering ethical, transparent, and people-centred recruitment services. As a trusted domestic helper agency, we bring a fresh, hands-on approach to employment services, focusing on compliance, clarity, and long-term suitability, as well as volume-driven placements.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-text/80 font-normal leading-relaxed">
          We work closely with employers and helpers to ensure expectations are clearly aligned from the start, especially for first-time employers, and that every domestic helper placement is made fairly, responsibly, and in accordance with Singapore's employment regulations.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-text/80 font-normal leading-relaxed">
          Alexis Employment supports recruitment and placement services, guiding employers through the entire process, from helper sourcing and screening to documentation, onboarding coordination, and post-placement support. As a Singapore maid agency, we place strong emphasis on fair employment practices, accurate job representation, and ethical recruitment standards.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-text/80 font-normal leading-relaxed">
          Our operations are built on regulatory compliance, transparency in fees and processes, and personalised service. We believe in growing responsibly, earning trust through consistent service quality, and building long-term relationships with employers, partners, and domestic helpers.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-text/80 font-normal leading-relaxed">
          At Alexis Employment, we are committed to serving with integrity and professionalism, and to contributing positively to Singapore's helpers ecosystem.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 reveal">
      
      <div class="p-10 bg-brand-cream border border-brand-blue/5 text-center">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-brand-blue mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm">
          <i data-lucide="award" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-text mb-3">Our Mission</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-brand-text/80 leading-relaxed font-normal">
          To connect every family in Singapore with a trusted, well-matched domestic helper through a process that is honest, compliant, and caring.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-10 bg-brand-cream border border-brand-blue/5 text-center">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-brand-blue mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm">
          <i data-lucide="eye" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-text mb-3">Our Vision</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-brand-text/80 leading-relaxed font-normal">
          To be Singapore's most trusted domestic helper agency, known for our integrity, personalised service, and commitment to both families and helpers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-10 bg-brand-cream border border-brand-blue/5 text-center">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-brand-blue mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm">
          <i data-lucide="heart" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-text mb-3">Our Values</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-brand-text/80 leading-relaxed font-normal">
          Transparency, ethical recruitment, genuine care for helpers and families alike, and full compliance with MOM regulations at every step.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Meet Our Founder Section -->
<section class="py-32 bg-brand-snow">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      
      <!-- Photo Column -->
      <div class="flex justify-center pt-16">
        <img 
          src="/alex-lee.jpeg" 
          alt="Alex Lee - Director & Founder"
          class="rounded-full w-64 h-64 object-cover object-top shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Bio Column -->
      <div>
        <span class="text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-blue font-bold mb-4 block">Meet Our Founder</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-brand-text tracking-tight mb-6">Alex Lee</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-blue font-bold mb-6">Director & Founder</p>
        <p class="text-brand-text/80 font-normal leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Hi, I'm Alex Lee, Director & Founder of Alexis Employment Agency. I bring over a decade of diverse experience spanning my time in the Republic of Singapore Navy, consumer sales, and corporate business development. My years in the Navy gave me a strong foundation in discipline, integrity, and commitment to excellence, values I carry into everything I do at Alexis Employment Agency today.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-text/80 font-normal leading-relaxed">
          Having worked directly with consumers across multiple industries, I understand what people truly need: clear communication, genuine care, and reliable service. I founded Alexis Employment Agency to bring these same standards to domestic helper placement, ensuring every family receives a personalised, transparent, and trusted experience from start to finish.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
